c: 2
v: 216
t: "Kulamulidwe kukwenu jenumanja kuputa ngondo kutendaga jalakwejo jili jakuŵenjedwa kukwenu, nambotu komboleka kuchiŵenga chindu kutendaga chili chambone kukwenu, soni nikomboleka kuchinonyela chindu kutendaga chili chakusakala kukwenu, sano Allah ni jwaakumanyilila, nambo ŵanganyammwe ngankumanyilila"